Open file manager: A toolbar button tooltip for opening the file browser that allows inserting an image or a file to the editor.
Cannot determine a category for the uplo: A message is displayed when CKEditor 5 cannot associate an image with any of the categories defined in CKBox while uploading an asset.
A message is displayed when the user is not authorised to access the CKBox workspace configured as default one.
Edit image: Image toolbar button tooltip for opening a dialog to manipulate the image.
A message is displayed when user try to close page while image is not processed yet on server.
